    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270452</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここが塔のてっぺん、かな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Is this the tower's summit? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270540</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>出てこい、悪い魔女！
観念しろーっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Come out you horrid magician! Stop hiding! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちっ……まったく、もう……
あ～、コホン……ンンッ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kids these days... Well, *cough* ahem *cough cough* </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ここまでよく来たな。
褒めてやろう</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is as far as you go. You're standing in my way. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>270792</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃが、おまえたちの命は
ここまでじゃ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is it! Your life shall come to an end right here! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我が魔力を結集し作り出した、
ミラクルドリームエックス！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Come forth, o guardian created
by my grand magical power. 
Miracle Dream X! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>271208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_030_060_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>これまでみたいに
簡単にはいかぬぞ！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Defeating this foe won't be an easy feat at all! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
